{
  "text": "These projects include structured event annotation for the domain of cancer biology, Japanese verb frame annotation, and genemutation-phenotype relation annotation. One prominent effort making use of BRAT is the BioNLP Shared Task 2011, 1 in which the tool was used in the annotation of the EPI and ID main task corpora [CITATION_1] . These two information extraction tasks involved the annotation of entities, relations and events in the epigenetics and infectious diseases subdomains of biology. Figure 5 shows an illustration of shared task annotations.",
